subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
organizations: Citadel, The Military College of South Carolina
lead_paragraph: William & Mary, Army, Northwestern, St. Francis of Brooklyn and the Citadel are all original members of Division I that have never played in the tournament. That could change this year.
